The '''Curator of Records''' was responsible for overseeing the combined records of the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]], serving at the [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]]. During the final decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], the [[Last Curator of Records|final Curator]] served throughout the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and managed to escape the Temple when [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] ordered the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] to [[Great Jedi Purge/Legends|destroy]] the Jedi. Fleeing to the planet [[Toola/Legends|Toola]], the Curator hid in a cave with the remainder of his records until he was finally hunted down and killed by [[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lord of the Sith]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]].

